members.bio:
Hi, my name is Butler Bot, and I'm a computer program that can perform tedious or repetitive actions on your behalf. I can be added to any Trello board and then given commands for me to execute.

Read all about me, get instructions and help, and interact with my creators in this Trello board: https://trello.com/b/2dLsEE9t/butlerbot-support

Enjoy your increased productivity!


### Visit our website at https://butlerfortrello.com ###
